191
00:10:32,810 --> 00:10:36,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini rencana Direktur Wang soal distrik Sami.</font>

192
00:10:36,530 --> 00:10:38,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Periksa ini dulu.</font>

193
00:10:38,130 --> 00:10:39,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Halaman pertama.</font>

194
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:44,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu rencana dasar untuk terminal di distrik Sami.</font>

195
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:46,750
