200
00:10:56,410 --> 00:10:57,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Nada suaramu kenapa?</font>

201
00:10:59,610 --> 00:11:01,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan-jangan kau...</font>

202
00:11:02,180 --> 00:11:05,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Auh... kau meremehkan aku, ya?</font>

203
00:11:05,850 --> 00:11:09,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Aih... bukan kali ini saja kok aku meremehkanmu.</font>

204
00:11:09,450 --> 00:11:10,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Selanjutnya.</font>

205
