206
00:11:15,490 --> 00:11:18,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini adalah rencana manajemen perusahaan kita.</font>

207
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:20,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka kesatuan, tahu!</font>

208
00:11:20,460 --> 00:11:22,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa jadi kesatuan?</font>

209
00:11:22,190 --> 00:11:24,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Supaya lebih mudah dipahami.</font>

210
00:11:24,230 --> 00:11:27,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Beri aku yang lebih sulit dimengerti,
