211
00:11:27,290 --> 00:11:29,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ini Presdir!</font>

212
00:11:29,060 --> 00:11:30,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuharap perusahaan kita tidak turun kelas.</font>

213
00:11:30,730 --> 00:11:32,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau bilang?</font>

214
00:11:32,450 --> 00:11:35,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mempertaruhkan tanganku, dalam tiga hari kau pasti kembali naik subway.</font>

215
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:37,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Wah... dasar!</font>

216
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:42,440
