217
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:45,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Memang apa suitnya ini?</font>

218
00:11:47,310 --> 00:11:49,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini mudah sekali.</font>

219
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Ki Doong-<i>ah</i>.</font>

220
00:12:07,750 --> 00:12:09,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak tidur, lho.</font>

221
00:12:16,410 --> 00:12:18,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Apaan!</font>

222
00:12:26,230 --> 00:12:29,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Ma Rin! Aku merindukanmu.</font>

223
00:12:30,850 --> 00:12:33,090
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Pekerjaanmu lancar?</i></font>

224
00:12:33,090 --> 00:12:35,160
