225
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:37,130
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Pekerjaannya lancar saja, kok.</i></font>

226
00:12:37,130 --> 00:12:38,870
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tapi, aku merindukanmu.</i></font>

227
00:12:39,330 --> 00:12:40,560
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku juga.</i></font>

228
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:43,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku ingin bertemu denganmu. Rindukan aku, ya.</i></font>

229
00:12:44,220 --> 00:12:46,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Sedang apa sih saat ibumu duduk di sini?</font>

230
00:12:46,460 --> 00:12:49,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebentar. Biar kukirim SMS ini dulu.</font>

231
00:12:49,090 --> 00:12:51,140
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku sedang makan di luar bersama Ibu.</i></font>

232
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:54,600
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Menyenangkan seandainya kau bisa ikut.</i></font>

233
00:12:59,850 --> 00:13:01,680
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Suamimu ini harus bekerja.</i></font>

234
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:05,640
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Lagi pula, ibumu menakutkan.</i></font>

235
00:13:16,450 --> 00:13:17,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, <i>Ahjussi</i>.</font>

236
00:13:20,260 --> 00:13:22,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei! Bicara juga padaku!</font>

237
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:27,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita perlu bicara selagi bertemu.
Memang aku ini dinding!?</font>

238
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sebabnya dia takut pada Ibu.</font>

239
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:33,550
<font color=#FFFF00>- Siapa?
