240
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:36,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau belum menjelaskan padanya?</font>

241
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:37,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah.</font>

242
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:40,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mengaku padanya kalau aku bohong pada Ibu soal perselingkuhannya.</font>

243
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:44,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Kudengar Ibu sampai bergulingan di tanah.</font>

244
00:13:45,470 --> 00:13:47,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh?</font>

245
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:49,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu keren.</font>

246
00:13:49,670 --> 00:13:52,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah Ibu pukul, dia berubah total.</font>

247
00:13:53,420 --> 00:13:58,160
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aigoo... </i>dasar!
