336
00:18:58,310 --> 00:19:00,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa sih tidak.</font>

337
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:04,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yakin ada seseorang yang akan membawakan aku payung.</font>

338
00:19:04,420 --> 00:19:06,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, aku ini orang sibuk (tidak bisa membawakanmu payung)!</font>

339
00:19:06,110 --> 00:19:08,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Ma Rin-<i>ah</i>!</font>

340
00:19:08,040 --> 00:19:10,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, Sayang!</font>

341
00:19:10,270 --> 00:19:11,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau di sini.</font>

342
00:19:11,380 --> 00:19:12,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pergi.</font>

343
00:19:12,520 --> 00:19:13,740
<font color=#FFFF00>- Sapalah!
