346
00:19:20,130 --> 00:19:23,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada orang lain di pihakku. Pria itu.</font>

347
00:19:23,290 --> 00:19:25,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, kenapa dia kabur begitu?</font>

348
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:26,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia memang kadang jadi aneh.</font>

349
00:19:28,730 --> 00:19:32,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, aku membawakanmu payung karena hujan turun.</font>

350
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:35,220
